# Marketaux — live financial news with photos (https://www.marketaux.com)
# 1. Create a free account, 2. copy your API token, 3. paste it below,
# 4. save this file as `.env` (not .env.example) and restart `npm run dev`.
# Without a key the site shows realistic demo articles so it never looks empty.
VITE_MARKETAUX_KEY=your_marketaux_api_key_here
